name_full: 弗雷迪·史密斯 Freddie Smith
birth_place: 美国,俄亥俄州,阿什塔比拉

last_movies.title: 新飞越比佛利 第三季

introduction: Freddie grew up as an only child and graduated in 2006 from Edgewood Senior High in Ashtabula, Ohio.He began his acting career in 2008, appearing in a cameo role in the paranormal series Medium playing a Senior Boy, uncredited during that episode.He appeared in the short film titled Weak Species co-starring Erik Smith and in the film One Wish released in 2010. He has also done commercials for Kay Jewelers and Verizon.He took up the role of Jackson "Sonny" Kiriakis developed by Leah Laiman, the first openly gay contracted character in the hit daytime soap opera.- IMDb Mini Biography By: RW
